### ðŸ§  Summary

This app:

* Allows users to sign up and log in.
* Lets users chat with GPT-4o-mini.
* Supports file uploads (CSV, images, docs).
* Automatically generates data visualizations from CSVs.
* Saves everything in a local SQLite database.

